The State Capture Commission is currently hearing Eskom related evidence from the former Eskom Board Chairperson, Dr Ben Ngubane. Earlier, the Commission of Inquiry into State Capture in Johannesburg has heard how external parties influenced the appointment and removal of some executives at Eskom. However, Ngubane told the commission that the removal of his predecessor Zola Tsotsi was for business and operational reasons Link to the stream: 